  "response": "Here are some popular and delicious date cake recipes:\n\n1. Classic Date Cake\n- Moist cake with chopped dates\n- Often includes nuts like walnuts\n- Can be served with caramel or cream sauce\n\n2. Sticky Toffee Pudding\n- Traditional British dessert\n- Dense cake with dates\n- Served with warm toffee sauce\n\n3. Iranian Date Cake (Rangi)\n- Uses dates, flour, and spices\n- Often includes cardamom and cinnamon\n- Traditionally served during celebrations\n\n4. Date and Walnut Loaf\n- Simple, dense cake\n- Great with tea or coffee\n- Contains chopped dates and walnuts\n\n5. Arabian Date Cake\n- Uses dates as primary sweetener\n- Often includes flour, eggs, and butter\n- Can be garnished with pistachios\n\n6. No-Bake Date Cake\n- Made with dates, nuts, and minimal baking\n- Often vegan and gluten-free\n- Uses a food processor\n\n7. Chocolate Date Cake\n- Combines chocolate and dates\n- Rich and decadent\n- Can be topped with ganache\n\nEach recipe offers a unique twist on incorporating dates into a delicious cake.",
